OL,3,CGovernment's energy support schemes
OL,4,C'undoubtedly successful' ` NAO
OL,6,FThe government's support schemes to
OL,7,Fprotect people and businesses from
OL,8,Fsoaring energy prices were
OL,9,F"undoubtedly successful", Whitehall's
OL,10,Fspending watchdog has said.
OL,12,FThe previous government introduced
OL,13,Feight different support schemes for
OL,14,Fhouseholds and businesses ` including
OL,15,Fthe Energy Price Guarantee ` in 2022
OL,16,Fand 2023 after Covid-19 and Russia's
OL,17,Finvasion of Ukraine caused average
OL,18,Fannual household bills to increase
OL,19,Ffrom #1,277 in the winter of 2021/22
OL,20,Fto more than #4,000 by the start of
OL,21,F2023.
