OL,3,CGovernment's energy support schemes
OL,4,C'undoubtedly successful' ` NAO
OL,6,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) said
OL,7,Fthe government deserved credit for
OL,8,Fworking quickly to introduce the
OL,9,Fschemes.
OL,11,FBut the NAO found "moving at speed"
OL,12,Fmeant the government had to accept
OL,13,Frisks to value for money and providing
OL,14,Funiversal support meant some people
OL,15,Freceived financial assistance they did
OL,16,Fnot need.
