OL,6,FBut DESNZ estimated that despite
OL,7,Fgovernment support around 238,000
OL,8,Fhouseholds fell into fuel poverty
OL,9,Fbetween 2022 and 2023.
OL,11,FAlthough the government quickly
OL,12,Fdistributed financial support to most
OL,13,Fhouseholds there was low take-up among
OL,14,Fharder-to-reach groups such as people
OL,15,Fliving on boats.
