OL,6,FFor households without a direct
OL,7,Frelationship with an electricity
OL,8,Fsupplier take-up was around one-fifth
OL,9,Fof DESNZ's provisional estimate of
OL,10,Fpotentially eligible recipients,
OL,11,Faccording to the report.
OL,13,FDESNZ was taking steps to understand
OL,14,Fwhat it could have done to improve
OL,15,Ftake-up while considering how a range
OL,16,Fof interventions might help mitigate
OL,17,Fthe risks of a future energy crisis.
