OL,3,CGovernment's energy support schemes
OL,4,C'undoubtedly successful' ` NAO
OL,6,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,7,F"The government acted quickly to
OL,8,Fprovide tens of billions of pounds of
OL,9,Fsupport to help protect people and
OL,10,Fbusinesses from soaring energy price
OL,11,Frises, with relatively low levels of
OL,12,Ffraud and error.
OL,14,F"DESNZ needs to prepare for future
OL,15,Fenergy price spikes and understand how
OL,16,Fany potential future interventions can
OL,17,Fbe provided in a way that maximises
OL,18,Fvalue for money.
